# ─── Embedded Wallet Configuration ──────────────────────────────────────────
# This package is a client-side (browser) library with no server-side
# environment variables. Configuration is passed programmatically via
# EmbeddedWalletConfig and WalletManagerConfig.
#
# If you embed this package in a server-rendered app, you may reference
# these variables at build time:

# Optional: override the default storage prefix used in IndexedDB / localStorage
EMBEDDED_WALLET_STORAGE_PREFIX=@cinacoin/embedded-wallet
